steps.html_instructions: Merge onto I-45 N via the ramp on the left to Dallas
Take exit 770C on the left to merge onto US-59 N toward Cleveland
Take the U.S. 59 N/Texas 287 Loop ramp to Nacogdoches

Merge onto US-59 N/S Medford Dr
Continue to follow US-59 N
Slight right onto the US 59 N/TX-224 Loop N ramp to Texarkana

Merge onto TX-224 Loop W/US-59 N/SE Stallings Dr
Continue to follow US-59 N

Turn left onto Texas Loop 436/TX-149 W
Continue to follow Texas Loop 436
Slight right onto the US-59 N ramp to Texarkana/I-30 W/Dallas

Take the exit onto I-30 E/US-59 N toward Little Rock/Ashdown
Continue to follow I-30 E
Entering Arkansas
Take exit 2B for Doctor Martin Luther King Junior Drive

Turn right onto Dr Martin Luther King Dr/M L King (signs for State Capitol Complex)
Continue to follow Dr Martin Luther King Dr
